Sappi Expects Its Third-Quarter Earnings to Be in Line With a Year Earlier

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-05-09T07:03:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-09/sappi-expects-its-third-quarter-earnings-to-be-in-line-with-a-year-earlier.html
Sappi Ltd. (SAP)  said it expects that its
results excluding special items for the third quarter to be in
line with the same three-month period a year earlier.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
